      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a great start. i actually need the essay to address the counter-arguments too, so it's more academic. one big criticism i keep seeing is that wealth redistribution goes against the idea of meritocracy—like, that people should be able to keep what they earn through hard work and that redistributing it is basically unfair to those who succeeded. how should i address that part? is the meritocracy argument actually a valid critique or is it just a way to ignore the systemic stuff you mentioned?",
